    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The Jet Black Metallic paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like finish free of any stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the black leather sport seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the interior still retains its factory-fresh scent. Every electronic component and switch functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is peak-performance, with a comprehensive service history exclusively through Porsche authorized centers and a mere 12,000 original miles. It comes equipped with the Premium Package, 20-inch Carrera S wheels, and the Bose Surround Sound system. This is a non-smoker, no-pet vehicle with a clean title and zero track time. Included in the sale are both original keys, the owner's manuals, and a thick folder of maintenance receipts. For the buyer who demands perfection, this Cayman represents the pinnacle of its class.",
