      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the zenith of naturally aspirated performance, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced. The valvetrain is shimmed to factory tolerances, and the rod bearings have been replaced preventatively to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The chassis remains flawlessly rigid, with a reinforced rear subframe mount and fresh bushings throughout. Power is transferred via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional traction and corner-exit torque. With a pristine undercarriage and factory-spec compression across all six cylinders, this is a turnkey, collector-grade specimen for the technical purist.",
